notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the httpd SRPM in CIQ Bridge for CentOS 7.9. It addresses 16 CVEs: CVE-2006-20001, CVE-2020-35452, CVE-2021-26690, CVE-2021-26691, CVE-2021-34798, and 11 more.
